                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-362-18690301 t18690301-362-punishment-56"></join>Two Year's Imprisonment each</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
